s interrupting your gameplay. It also lacks a rescue CD or program to restore your computer in case it is attacked by malware. Both of these features are standard with higher-ranked solutions in our Mac antivirus comparison.","There aren&#39;t many tech support options either. No telephone numbers are listed on the website or in the program. You can use the online support form to submit a ticket, and support personnel will then email you a response. You can access documentation on its website or find answers to your questions on the discussion forums."]},"id":"ebdea50a-cdd2-4d12-be7a-2f046fc586b2","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"49413c89-00c1-46f9-a561-7161797cb4e4","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["ClamXav 2 had the lowest score for protection from the independent laboratory AV-Test, though it still detected 90 percent of known malware threats. It scans both email and USB files and doesn&#39;t use too much of your computer&#39;s resources while running. The interface is clean and easy to use, though it lacks many of the features commonly included in higher-ranked Mac antivirus software."]},"id":"e78b909d-1975-40e6-9abe-3de4a50b0bed","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_68463","url":"/clamxav-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"nicole-johnston","url":"/author/nicole-johnston","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Nicole Johnston","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"nR6fcTbvfudgncYJbhzqDB","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2016-09-27T13:36:44Z","datePublished":"2016-09-27T13:36:44Z","name":"ClamXav 2 Personal","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product.","review":{"rating":54,"verdict":"ClamXav is a basic virus protection solution that doesn&#039;t include too many features, resulting in a low loss of computer performance.","pros":["This program